readme:
# Improved Dusk Syntax

A dark syntax theme inspired by Xcode's Dusk theme for Atom.

@shenmin - And some minor changed (colors) according to my preferences. :)

# Syntax Preview

![A preview of Dusk Syntax](https://raw.github.com/shenmin/dusk-syntax/master/screenshots/preview.png)

# Installation

From the command line:

```
$ apm install improved-dusk-syntax
```

# Acknowledgments

Thanks to the following people for their hard work and contributions to the packages mentioned above.

- @jamesejr
- @cannikin
- @fundon
- @danbrooker
